{
  "id": "69b3cbeb26f1ff31e8ca1865",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:データベース消費",
  "created": 1773390864,
  "updated": 1773391136,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b3cbeb26f1ff31e8ca1865",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:データベース消費",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390864,
      "updated": 1773390864
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1000000000008eef1e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390864,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef1f",
      "text": "ねえねえ二人とも〜。今日はさ、「[データベース消費]」ってやつについて語ろうぜって先生に言われたんだけどさ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef20",
      "text": "ぶっちゃけ、オタク文化の話らしいんよね。アニメとかゲーム好きのうちらにはドンピシャ案件じゃね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef22",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef23",
      "text": "まあ……そうなのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef24",
      "text": "「消費」という言葉を聞くと、どこか少し冷たい響きもありますけれど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef25",
      "text": "けれど物語やキャラクターを愛する気持ちの流れを考える言葉なのだとしたら、興味深いものですわね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef27",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef28",
      "text": "定義から整理しておこう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef2a",
      "text": "「データベース消費」は社会学者・[東浩紀]が提示した概念。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390887
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef2b",
      "text": "ポストモダン以降、物語（大きなストーリー）よりも、キャラクター要素のデータベースが消費されるという理論だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef2d",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef2e",
      "text": "https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/データベース消費",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef30",
      "text": "要するに、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef31",
      "text": "作品全体のストーリーより",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef32",
      "text": "属性の組み合わせ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef33",
      "text": "でキャラクターが消費される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef35",
      "text": "例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef36",
      "text": " ツンデレ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef37",
      "text": " メガネ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef38",
      "text": " 妹キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef39",
      "text": " 猫耳",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef3a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef3b",
      "text": "こうした要素の集合を人は楽しむ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef3d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef3e",
      "text": "あーーーなるほどね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef3f",
      "text": "つまりさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef41",
      "text": "「このキャラの人生がどうなるか」より",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef42",
      "text": "「このキャラの属性が神」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef43",
      "text": "みたいな感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef45",
      "text": "例えばさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef46",
      "text": "妹＋ゲーム好き＋元気",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef47",
      "text": "とか、完全にワイのカテゴリじゃんｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef49",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef4a",
      "text": "まさにそれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef4b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef4c",
      "text": "データベースは、言い換えるとキャラ設定の巨大なカタログ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef4d",
      "text": "作品は、そのカタログからパーツを組み合わせて作られる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef4f",
      "text": "ゲームで言えばキャラメイクに近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef50",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef51",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef52",
      "text": "まあ……それは、なんだかお料理のようですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef53",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef54",
      "text": "同じお野菜でも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef55",
      "text": "煮るか焼くか、香辛料を変えるかで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef56",
      "text": "まったく違う味わいになりますでしょう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef57",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef58",
      "text": "キャラクターの性格や外見も、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef59",
      "text": "そうした材料のように組み合わされている……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef5a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef5b",
      "text": "そう思うと、少し可愛らしく感じられます。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef5c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef5d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef5e",
      "text": "わかる〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef5f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef60",
      "text": "てか最近のソシャゲとか、完全にそれじゃね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef61",
      "text": "「新キャラ追加！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef62",
      "text": "って言われたらストーリーより先に",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef63",
      "text": " 見た目",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef64",
      "text": " 属性",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef65",
      "text": " 性格",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef66",
      "text": "見ちゃうもんｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef67",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef68",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef69",
      "text": "良い観察だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef6b",
      "text": "実際、東浩紀は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef6c",
      "text": "90年代以降のオタク文化でその傾向が強まったと指摘している。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef6e",
      "text": "たとえば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef6f",
      "text": " ガンダム → 世界観・ストーリー中心",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef70",
      "text": " エヴァ以降 → キャラクター中心",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef71",
      "text": "という分析もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef73",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef74",
      "text": "https://www.h-up.com/books/isbn978-4-309-24506-3.html",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef75",
      "text": "（『動物化するポストモダン』）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef76",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef77",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef78",
      "text": "けれど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef7a",
      "text": "少しだけ思うのですが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef7b",
      "text": "キャラクターの要素だけを愛するというのは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef7c",
      "text": "どこか寂しい気もいたしますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef7d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef7e",
      "text": "物語というのは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef7f",
      "text": "人が歩んできた道のりを見守るようなもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef81",
      "text": "そこに心を寄せる時間も、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef82",
      "text": "やはり大切なのではないでしょうか。（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef83",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef84",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef85",
      "text": "あーそれな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef87",
      "text": "ストーリー神な作品って、やっぱ別格よね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef89",
      "text": "でもさ、オタクって",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef8a",
      "text": "「キャラ萌え」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef8b",
      "text": "↓",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef8c",
      "text": "「二次創作」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef8d",
      "text": "みたいな流れも多いじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef8f",
      "text": "これもデータベース消費ってこと？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef91",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef92",
      "text": "その可能性は高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef93",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef94",
      "text": "二次創作は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef95",
      "text": "既存のキャラ要素を再利用する文化。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef96",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef97",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef98",
      "text": "キャラデータベース",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef99",
      "text": "↓",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef9a",
      "text": "ファンが再構築",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef9b",
      "text": "という構造になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef9d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef9e",
      "text": "まあ……それは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eef9f",
      "text": "物語が種のように広がってゆく姿にも見えますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa1",
      "text": "誰かが蒔いた小さな種が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa2",
      "text": "別の人の心の土壌で芽を出す……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa4",
      "text": "そう考えると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa5",
      "text": "とても温かな循環のようにも思えます。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa8",
      "text": "あやさんの表現、文学すぎて草ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefa9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefaa",
      "text": "でも確かに、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefab",
      "text": "オタク文化ってみんなで作る感じあるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefad",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefae",
      "text": "ここで一度まとめる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefaf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb0",
      "text": "データベース消費のポイント",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb1",
      "text": " 1. 物語よりキャラ属性が重視される",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb2",
      "text": " 2. キャラは「要素の組み合わせ」として理解される",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb3",
      "text": " 3. ファンもそのデータベースを利用する（二次創作など）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb5",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb6",
      "text": "物語中心文化 → キャラ要素中心文化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb7",
      "text": "への変化と言える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefb9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefba",
      "text": "なるほどな〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefbb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefbc",
      "text": "つまり今のオタクって",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefbd",
      "text": "「ストーリーを読む人」ってより",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefbe",
      "text": "「キャラ設定データを楽しむ人」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefbf",
      "text": "って感じなんか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc1",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc2",
      "text": "ですが……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc4",
      "text": "きっと人の心は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc5",
      "text": "データだけでは満たされないものですわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc7",
      "text": "いつかそのキャラクターが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc8",
      "text": "どんな悲しみを知り、どんな喜びを見つけるのか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefc9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefca",
      "text": "そうした物語を知りたくなるのも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefcb",
      "text": "また人の自然な気持ちでしょうから。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefcc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefcd",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefce",
      "text": "同意する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefcf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd0",
      "text": "データベース消費は文化の一面を説明する理論。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd1",
      "text": "すべてを説明するわけではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd3",
      "text": "むしろ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd4",
      "text": " 物語消費",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd5",
      "text": " データベース消費",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd6",
      "text": "両方が共存していると考えるのが妥当。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefd9",
      "text": "おお、なんか今日めっちゃ理解できたわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefda",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefdb",
      "text": "つまりオタク文化って",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefdc",
      "text": "ストーリー勢 vs キャラ勢",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefdd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefde",
      "text": "って感じで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefdf",
      "text": "どっちも楽しみ方としてアリってことね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe1",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe2",
      "text": "ええ、きっとそうですわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe4",
      "text": "物語を旅する楽しみも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe5",
      "text": "キャラクターを愛でる楽しみも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe6",
      "text": "どちらも同じ本棚に並べられるものですもの。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe8",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefe9",
      "text": "結論としてはこうだろう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefeb",
      "text": "文化は常に進化する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefed",
      "text": "そして私たちは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefee",
      "text": "物語も、データベースも、両方の世界に住んでいる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eefef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eeff0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eeff1",
      "text": "おおー締めが中二でカッケーｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eeff2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eeff3",
      "text": "じゃあ今日はこのへんで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
      "id": "69b3cc1100000000008eeff4",
      "text": "オタク文化トーク、またやろーぜ！ 🎮✨",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773390865,
      "updated": 1773390865
    },
    {
